snippet.title: Brawlhalla x Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles Reveal Trailer | #UbiFWD
snippet.description:
Cowabunga! On 16th June, Raphael, Michelangelo, Leonardo and  Donatello will be playable in Brawlhalla as Epic Crossovers! 

Their arrival will ninja-kick off an in-game event featuring a new game mode, a new map and plenty of new exclusive cosmetics!

To catch the latest Brawlhalla news and content, be sure to follow us on:

Twitter: https://twitter.com/brawlhalla
Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/brawlhalla
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Brawlhalla/
YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/Brawlhalla
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/brawlhalla/
Discord: https://discord.com/invite/brawlhalla

Discover Brawlhalla, one of the most played fighting games on PC, PS4, PS5, Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S, Nintendo Switch and Mobile! 

Play it for free!
Visit the website: https://www.ubisoft.com/r/Brawlhalla
